org.apache.ignite.ml.math.impls.vector

Class AbstractReadOnlyVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.math.impls.vector.AbstractVector
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.math.impls.vector.AbstractReadOnlyVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Destroyable, MetaAttributes, StorageOpsMetrics, Vector
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstantVector, RandomVector

    public abstract class AbstractReadOnlyVector
extends AbstractVector
    This class provides a helper implementation of the read-only implementation of Vector interface to minimize the effort required to implement it. Subclasses may override some of the implemented methods if a more specific or optimized implementation is desirable.
    See Also:
